{"tid":1163822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"各位娛樂台巴絲知唔知道64嗰日做咩好","createTime":"2019-05-20T16:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T08:05:35.000Z","uid":231132,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2ecc0f34525eeb8372e7fd4ec8bb1a44ea0a40eb","tid":1163822,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"當然係聽宇宙少女新專！<br />\nEverything happened in a flash<br />\nIt bloomed in my heart<br />\nI call it love<br />\n(๑&bull;̀ㅂ&bull;́)و✧<br />\n<br />\n宇宙少女6月4日回歸歌謠界。<br />\nStarship Entertainment18日在官方SNS頻道上公開了宇宙少女的特別專輯海報，預告了突襲回歸。<br />\n公開的照片中，在清涼大海邊的沙灘上出現的宇宙少女，吸引了人們的視線。成員們一起手牽手向大海奔跑的背影，增添了他們獨有的愉快魅力。特別是在炎熱的天氣裡，華麗的夏日時尚和多彩的髮色讓人心曠神怡。<br />\n同時公開了&quot;For The Summer 2019.06.04. 6PM WJSN COMING SOON&quot;的文本，更加增加了人們對特別專輯的好奇心。宇宙少女將於6月4日發表特別專輯《For The Summer》，目前正在為回歸做最後的準備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nTuJOAv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnTuJOAv.jpg&h=9fa25767&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e22a84ca015bb8419b0e39ef7d85a2289c47def1","tid":1163822,"uid":159444,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:00:10.000Z","msg":"(突發) 金鐘圖part 2 !!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1163619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1163619</a><br />\n<br />\n政府絕對唔會讓步 讓一細步都唔得 因為佢哋唔可以俾你成功 因為只要成功左一次個無力感就會消失<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1159755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1159755</a>"},{"pid":"03f5048a0fd58693138995d638a7550ea4681059","tid":1163822,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:05:42.000Z","msg":"沙灘 = 天安門<br />\n中國妹對H奶 = 坦克<br />\n其他成員 = 示威者"},{"pid":"a14c767d57c4d7b212de6688dea3a7831ce64f54","tid":1163822,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:13:45.000Z","msg":"唔怪得冇支那成員份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ab8fe7f6e4bf9